        '<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:24pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">中原大地上的风雪，一场接一场，但风雪总是阻挡不了那些追寻春天的热望，就像寒风中静静绽放在枝头的梅花，就像皑皑白雪下依然生长的小草，就像全国各地为了感受中原魅力蜂拥而至的游客，就像近日那些出现在寒冬清晨抑或傍晚的跑者们，他们一边奔跑，一边热切地等待着一个关于</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">“春天”的讯息。</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:Calibri;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:24pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:24pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">现在，这个讯息来了：第十六届郑开马拉松赛将于</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">2024</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">年</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">3</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">月</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">31</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">日正式开赛，今日</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">16</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">点</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">16</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">分报名通道正式开启！</span></span>\n</p>'),
       (2, 1, '2024-05-21 10:20:25', '关于对2024郑开马拉松赛违规选手曹某的处罚公告',
        '<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:华文仿宋;font-size:16pt;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">根据选手反映、录像、图片材料证明，经组委会核查，在</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;2024&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:华文仿宋;font-size:16pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">郑开马拉松赛举行过程中，亲子马拉松选手曹某（参赛号码：</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">0978）未按照规定在亲子赛道参赛，私自进入马拉松赛道违规参赛，违反了《2024郑开马拉松赛竞赛规程》的相关规定，造成了不良社会影响。</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:华文仿宋;font-size:16pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:华文仿宋;font-size:16pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp; 为保证赛事公平公正、树立良好赛风赛纪，给予选手曹某如下处罚：禁止参加</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">2025、2026郑开马拉松赛。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">希望跑者们尊重体育精神，遵守赛事规则，共同营造公正良好、积极向上的马拉松及路跑赛事环境。</span>\n</p>\n<div>\n	<br />\n</div>'),
       (3, 1, '2024-05-21 10:23:44', '2024郑开马拉松赛竞赛规程',
