size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">欢乐跑（包含情侣跑、亲子跑项目）开封段：</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">8:30</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（三）比赛地点</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松：郑开大道</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">半程马拉松、</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">欢乐跑（郑州段）</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">：郑州市</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">欢乐跑（开封段）：开封市</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">七</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">、竞赛项目</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">（一）马拉松（</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">42.195公里）</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">（二）半程马拉松（</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">21.0975公里）</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（三）欢乐跑（包含亲子跑和情侣跑）</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">八、比赛路线</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松起点：郑州市郑开大道白沙服务区（起点）</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松终点：开封市</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">、</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">半程马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">比赛线路</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">：</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">郑开大道</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">九</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">、竞赛办法</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（一）执行规则</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">按照中国田径协会审定的《田径竞赛规则</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">2018-2019》《世界田联竞赛与技术规则》《世界田联路跑赛事标牌规则2023》、中国田径协会路跑赛事管理办法及本次比赛规程执行。</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（二）比赛检录</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">1、所有选手须正确佩戴本届赛事号码布；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2、大众选手至少在赛前60分钟到达指定区域进行检录集结；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">3、专业运动员须在赛前30分钟到起点区域专门检录区进行检录；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">4、不允许后区进入前区检录起跑，前区可进入后区检录起跑；如违反则取消该选手成绩和排名。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（三）起跑顺序</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">马拉松、半程马拉松起点：</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">按特邀运动员、专业运动员、荣誉跑友、</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">大众参赛者</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">（按个人成绩分区站位）、半程马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">的顺序分区检录集结，各区域间距</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">10米。</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">注：为保证非竞速轮椅参赛者和其他参赛者的安全，非竞速轮椅参赛者出发位置位于大众参赛者队尾，请听从裁判及志愿者引导，有序出发。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\">欢乐跑</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\">（包含情侣跑、亲子跑）</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\">起点：爱心领跑方阵在前，其他选手随后。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（四）发令</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">采用一枪发令同时起跑的办法。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（五）计时办法</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">1、马拉松、半程马拉松项目采用感应器计时并为这两个项目的参赛者提供计时芯片，芯片将在参赛物品领取现场与号码布同时发放；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2、在起点、每5公里点、21.0975公里点、折返点和终点均设有计时感应地毯，选手行进过程中必须逐一通过所有的地面计时感应地毯，缺少任何一个计时点的成绩，将不予排名；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋