n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">十</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">、参赛办法</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（一）参赛者年龄要求</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">1、马拉松项目年龄限20岁以上（2004年12月31日之前出生）</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2、半程马拉松项目年龄限16岁以上（2008年12月31日之前出生）</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">3、欢乐跑（含亲子跑、情侣跑）项目限8岁以上（2016年12月31日之前出生）</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">备注：参赛选手须持有效证件（身份证、护照、军官证等）按照各项目的年龄规定进行报名。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">、半程</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">选手在领取参赛物料时需提供医院开具体检证明（包含：</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">血压</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">、心电图）或提供</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">202</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">-202</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">3</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">年参加中国田径协会认证的任意一场马拉松赛半程（含）以上成绩证明复印件。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">16岁以下未成年人参赛，组委会需要求其监护人或法定代理人签署参赛免责声明，且必须有一名监护人</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">报相同项目</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">陪同参加欢乐跑。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（二）参赛者身体状况要求</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松赛是一项大强度长距离的竞技运动，也是一项高风险的竞技项目，对参赛者身体状况有较高的要求，参赛者应提前进行身体体检，有长期参加跑步锻炼的基础。参赛者可根据自己的身体状况和能力，选择</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">马拉松、半程马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">和欢乐跑其中的一个项目报名参加。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">有以下疾病患者不宜参加比赛：</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">1、先天性心脏病和风湿性心脏病患者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2、高血压和脑血管疾病患者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">3、心肌炎和其他心脏病患者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">4、冠状动脉病患者和严重心律不齐者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">5、血糖过高或过少的糖尿病患者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">6、赛前两周出现发热咳嗽等病状者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">7、赛前一晚大量饮用烈性酒或睡眠不足者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">8、患有感染性疾病未痊愈者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">9、妊娠；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">10、其它不适合运动的疾病患者。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">在比赛中，因个人身体及其它个人原因导致的人身损害和财产损失，由参赛者个人承担责任。组委会要求参赛者提前去相应医疗机构进行健康体检，身体健康者可报名参加。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（三）赛事声明</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">1、本届赛事路线、赛事饮水站、赛事厕所等设置不适宜选手推婴儿车参赛，为充分保护全体参赛者人身安全，本届赛事禁止婴儿车进入赛道，组委会有权将婴儿车移出赛道。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2、本届赛事不设竞速轮椅组，竞速轮椅不得上赛道参赛，所获成绩不予录取名次。非竞速轮椅参赛者除需在官网或APP正常报名外，还需登录赛事官网下载《非竞速轮椅参赛者申请表》，具体报名流程详见《报名须知》。未经组委会审核同意，擅自参赛所产生的后果，由参赛者本人负责。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（四）报名办法</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">1、本次赛事总参赛规模为49000人，其中马拉松13000</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">人</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">，半程马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">16000人，欢乐跑20000人。所有选手须登录赛事官方网站（www.zkmarathon.com）或关注赛事官方微信公众号</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">“</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">郑开马拉松</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">”</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（微信号</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">：</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">zk_marathon）按相关要求进行报名。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2、马拉松、半程马拉松项目报名人数超过限定名额后，将以抽签方式确定参赛资格。欢乐跑（含情侣跑、亲子跑）项目报满为止。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">3、可直接获得参赛资格的对象</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">（</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">1）组委会邀请的选手；</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">（</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">2）郑开马拉松赛荣誉跑友</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">（</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">3）个人成绩达到</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">“</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2024郑开马拉松成绩直通标准</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;li