ustify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">注：按净计时成绩排名，奖金和名次对应发放，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">以居民身份证号确定河南籍</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（三）欢乐跑项目</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">欢乐跑（含情侣跑、亲子跑）项目不录取名次，不设置奖项与奖金。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28.1pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（四）领奖办法</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">1、现场不发放奖金，获奖者名单将在官网公示10个工作日。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">2、马拉松与半程马拉松项目的名次奖，如无疑义，获奖运动员奖金打入预留银行卡。如果发现兴奋剂检测有问题者，取消该名次，后面名次不递补。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">3、河南籍选手奖与年龄组奖，领取奖金请提交本人有效的银行卡号、本人签名的身份证复印件及联系电话，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">领奖有效期为正式公布获奖名单后</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">20天内，逾期未办理者按弃奖处理。</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">公示期内如对获奖者比赛成绩有异议，请联系组委会办公室并提供真实有效的证据。凡被举报违反竞赛规则和规程相关规定者，经调查取证确认事实则取消录取名次，其被取消的名次可以递补。联系电话</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">/传真：0371-86667787。</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">4、河南籍选手奖不包含中国田协注册运动员（专业运动员）。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">5、如同时获得多项奖励，则只奖励最高奖项，名次不递补。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">6、所有奖金将按照中华人民共和国税法的有关规定收取选手20%个人所得税，由组委会代收代缴。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">7、马拉松与半程马拉松项目的参赛选手，关门时间内完赛者可获得奖牌一枚、纪念品，并可在比赛结束5个工作日后登陆郑开马拉松赛官方网站打印成绩证书。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:32.15pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">十</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">二</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\">、处罚办法</span></b><b style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:32px;font-size:16pt;\"></span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">组委会将对起点、马拉松路线和终点进行录像监控，在比赛期间出现下列问题之一，比赛裁判员有权中止选手的比赛并当场没收违规选手的号码布，取消其比赛资格，赛后由组委会视情节轻重分别给予参赛选手取消郑开马拉松比赛成绩、禁赛</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">1-5年及终身禁赛等处罚，并报请中国田径协会追加处罚：</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（一）以虚假年龄或虚假身份报名；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">（二）一名选手同时携带</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">2枚以上（包括2枚）芯片参加比赛(包括男选手携带女选手芯片)；</span></span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（三）以接力方式完成比赛；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（四）不按规定的起跑顺序在非指定区域起跑；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（五）起跑有违反规则行为；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（六）关门时间到后不听劝阻、不停止比赛或退出比赛后又插入赛道；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（七）没有沿规定路线跑完全程，绕近道或乘交通工具（汽车、自行车、人力三轮、滑板等）以及途中插入等形式完成比赛；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（八）不按规定要求重复通过终点、未跑完全程私自通过终点及利用其它赛事或未佩戴号码布和本次比赛芯片领取完赛物品、完赛奖牌；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（九）私自涂改、遮挡号码布；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（十）不服从赛事工作人员指挥，干扰赛事，聚众闹事、打架斗殴；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（十一）中国田协公布的禁赛者；</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">（十二）其他违反规则规定的行为。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:28pt;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-wrap:wrap;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n		<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;line-height:28px;font-size:14pt;\">其中，利用虚假信息获取参